ong></i>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tough but <strong>VERY</strong> addictive gameplay<br></li><li> Evolving environment - fall back to the previous locations over and over again - discovering something new every time<br></li><li> Failure is progress<br></li><li> Anywhere between 10 and ∞ hours of gameplay<br></li><li> Countless distinct locations<br></li><li> Optional quests<br></li><li> You can throw goats and chickens around<br></li><li> Flick your mouse and dunk<br></li><li> 2.5 endings<br></li><li> makes you <i>feel</i> like Sisyphus</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is SoS?</h2><br><strong><i>Salvation of Sisyphus</i></strong> is a punishing, foddian, climbing (and mostly falling) platformer where your only friend is a pet rock and where failure leads to change. Flick the rock with accuracy. Catch it in the air so it does not fall down. Be careful not to fall yourself. <br>As you progress through this game, you will be able to find your inner peace by embracing negative emotions such as your rage and resentment towards the developer of this frustrating adventure!<br><br>MAY SALVATION COME!",
